{"tid":1487652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】老 共 想 學 人 攪 炒？","createTime":"2019-08-19T10:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T13:59:23.000Z","uid":64946,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e205a5115626e3934c04bf0eeb88a0d8d8f461d5","tid":1487652,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:57:07.000Z","msg":"曾鈺成話中共情願攪炒，戴返頭盔先我唔排除呢個可能性，但基本上係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>冇可能</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知唔知所謂愛國撚入面有幾多<span style=\"color: red;\">先</span>係信國家經濟強大，<span style=\"color: red;\">後</span>先愛國？ <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>錢同愛國係直接掛鉤架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span><br />\n老共要攬炒等於破壞呢班人嘅信仰，到時就真係遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都知香港係老共春袋，鄧小平強硬收返好大原因都係為錢，其次先係主權<br />\n64個環境條件同今日嘅香港冇得比，呢個唔洗解釋都明<br />\n一個岩岩開始發展，一個係發展好哂 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>一句講哂，dllm 開左真槍先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算死都係你班仆街權貴高官死先，<br />\n香港人未撚驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nanyway 曾鈺成條仆街真係好撚識講野 不得不防<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b40eb3e4ac8629a113678dd9dd543ad1c41545d","tid":1487652,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:02:37.000Z","msg":"1/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee956212c82c269f3c2aef604e857642cd6738a","tid":1487652,"uid":9315,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"老共攬炒方式只有一種  就係失勢個陣向全球發射核彈<br />\n寧願冚球剷都唔願好似蘇聯咁交出權力<br />\n大家睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa010a79a246a616424d22a9e05b645cdb7a5b11","tid":1487652,"uid":64946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5ee956212c82c269f3c2aef604e857642cd